OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLondonderry: Apology after 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpupils carried in luggage  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Farea of bus                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Translink has apologised after a number
OL,6, of schoolchildren were carried in the  
OL,7, luggage compartment of a moving bus.   
OL,9,FThe incident, first reported in the    
OL,10,FBelfast Telegraph, happened in         
OL,11,FLondonderry on Friday morning.         
OL,13,FThe Oakgrove Integrated College pupils 
OL,14,Fwere carried in the luggage area "for a
OL,15,Fshort period," said Translink.         
OL,17,F"This obviously should never have      
OL,18,Fhappened and we apologise unreservedly 
OL,19,Ffor it," said a spokesman.             
